<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_e8d9c8a45ba7.aspx"><b>周颂·烈文</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsone8d9c8a45ba7">
烈文辟公，锡兹祉福。惠我无疆，子孙保之。无封靡于尔邦，维王其崇之。<br />念兹戎功，继序其皇之。无竞维人，四方其训之。不显维德，百辟其刑之。於乎，前王不忘！
